<plot>Boy Wonder is the story of Sean Donovan, a young boy who's life is dramatically altered when he witnesses his mother's death in a brutal car jacking. Sean grows up into a strong young man, and at age 17 continues to search for his mother's killer. The boundaries between justice and revenge begin to blur, and Sean finds himself drawn into an underworld. While investigating a series of vigilante murders, new homicide detective, Teresa Ames, takes interest in Sean and his case. Yet the closer Teresa gets to Sean, the more her suspicions start to rise. Teresa and Sean engage in a twisting game of cat and mouse, allies by day enemies at night.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?081121</url></doc>
